Depends: python3, python3-venv, python3-pip
Description: BNG Monitor — Web dashboard for VPP/Accel-PPP monitoring
 FastAPI-based web dashboard for real-time monitoring of BNG stack:
 PPPoE sessions, policer traffic, RADIUS, alerts, and history.
 Runs on port 8877 by default.
